Localization.Name: Stor*All Big Box Model H2
Localization.Description:
Manufacturer: Stor*All
Item Type: Storage

Designed for the Hornet F7C Mk II, the Stor*All Big Box model H2 replaces the turret system of the military-spec craft with a respectable cargo hold.
